        "action": "Make PIP awards subject to a letter from a persons medical team only.",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "PIP awards are currently subject to an assessment with a healthcare representative. These people are unaware of the majority of medical conditions presented to them. I propose that a person applying for PIP, should be awarded this based on a report produced by their medical team looking after them.",
